            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "俄烏戰爭︱烏情報機關：普京準備日內宣布打勝仗",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"普京周五在莫斯科一個科技論壇上發言。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4ee536de7520152fee22dff57a3473d6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022202372673857.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">普京周五在莫斯科一個科技論壇上發言。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>烏克蘭總統澤連斯基近日跟美國特朗普公開罵戰，且烏國受到美國壓力要求盡快達成俄烏和平協議後，烏國軍情機關指，俄羅斯總統普京正準備於下周一之前宣布打贏這場曠日持久的俄烏戰爭。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"普京周五在莫斯科一個科技論壇上發言。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/56de2189249cde9eb967ecdb6d78ae5b/2025-02/0_WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-22_at_02_32_28_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        普京周五在莫斯科一個科技論壇上發言。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"烏總統澤連斯基。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5f5de18a25470657a5b46f78e0cb9c4a/2025-02/1_WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-22_at_02_27_35.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        烏總統澤連斯基。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"烏克蘭炮兵向俄軍陣地開火。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e655a492aedc8988bc34e87f4b9523c/2025-02/3_WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-22_at_02_28_10.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        烏克蘭炮兵向俄軍陣地開火。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"烏克蘭赫爾松市建築物因俄軍襲擊而嚴重損毀。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6369bffb11d4e6ecf84e4978ef8b70db/2025-02/4_WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-22_at_02_29_09.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        烏克蘭赫爾松市建築物因俄軍襲擊而嚴重損毀。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"烏總統澤連斯基去年九月會晤特朗普。網圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/986233e6b792405613838ee21efd4afb/2025-02/5_WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-22_at_02_30_26.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        烏總統澤連斯基去年九月會晤特朗普。網圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>據烏國軍事情報機構GUR稱，預計普京在一項新聲明中，將把情況描述為不僅是俄對烏的勝利，也是俄對北約的勝利，且會將這場戰爭描述為西方更廣泛的失敗。\n\n</p>\n<p>2025年2月24日(星期一)是俄烏戰爭爆發滿三週年的日子。GUR機構周五稱，「俄羅斯準備在2月24日這個日子到來前，宣布對烏克蘭戰爭的所謂『勝利』。」\n\n</p>\n<p>「此外，那些計劃還可能包括『俄羅斯戰勝北約』，因為莫斯科的宣傳長期以來一直將對烏克蘭的戰爭描述為與北約的戰爭。」\n\n</p>\n<p>這項舉措（如果得以實施）是在唐納德·川普及其政府為結束這場戰爭而採取的激烈行動背景下做出的，但歐洲和烏克蘭擔心，這項協議將為俄羅斯帶來優勢，獎勵普丁的軍事侵略行為。\n\n</p>\n<p>本週，美國總統對烏克蘭總統作出了嚴厲批評，指責後者挑起這場戰爭。澤連斯基則指特朗普成了俄羅斯假新聞攻勢的目標。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054226/即時-國際-俄烏戰爭︱烏情報機關-普京準備日內宣布打勝仗",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-22 02:46:24",
